#Surge_TencentMeeting.list___________________________
# NAME: TencentMeeting (腾讯会议)
# REPO: https://github.com/www011215/Surge_rule_list
# DESC: Route Tencent Meeting traffic to DIRECT so signaling / media stay
#       inside CN. Domains and IPs are merged from:
#         (a) verified strings inside /Applications/TencentMeeting.app/
#             (3.43.10.444 framework binaries),
#         (b) Surge virtual-IP DB observations on a live PID,
#         (c) Tencent Meeting official firewall whitelist
#             (https://meeting.tencent.com/support/topic/1929/).
# DESC: 故意排除的共享基础设施（避免误伤其他腾讯系产品）：
#       *.weixin.qq.com / *.wx.qq.com / mp.weixin.qq.com (微信登录共享)
#       captcha.qq.com / *.gtimg.com (通用验证码)
#       account/identity/workspace/oneid.tencent.com (腾讯统一身份)
#       *.qpic.cn / *.myqcloud.com 全量 SUFFIX (CDN 共享给海量租户)
#       *.tim.qq.com / *.imtt.qq.com (TIM SDK 共享)
# PROCESS-NAME: 1 (macOS only; Surge for iOS ignores PROCESS-NAME)
# DOMAIN: 5
# DOMAIN-SUFFIX: 11
# IP-CIDR: 114
# TOTAL: 131

PROCESS-NAME,/Applications/TencentMeeting.app/

# --- DOMAIN: TencentMeeting-exclusive subdomains under shared parents ---
DOMAIN,down-30005.sz.gfp.tencent-cloud.com
DOMAIN,yun.tim.qq.com
DOMAIN,tencentmeeting.txdocs.qq.com
DOMAIN,meeting-75420.gzc.vod.tencent-cloud.com
DOMAIN,wemeetvirtualbg-75586.gzc.vod.tencent-cloud.com

# --- DOMAIN-SUFFIX: TencentMeeting private domains ---
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,meeting.tencent.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,meeting.qq.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,wemeet.tencent.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,wemeet.qq.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,tencentmeeting.cn
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,voovmeeting.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,medialab.qq.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,im.qcloud.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,prtc.tencent.com
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,picgzc.qpic.cn
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,pictestsz.qpic.cn

